  "content": "  <details open>\r\n    <summary>⛩️ 종교활동</summary>\r\n    <div class=\"content\">\r\n      <details open>\r\n        <summary>🔮 대종교</summary>\r\n        <div class=\"content\">\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><strong>지도자</strong>: 나철, 오기호</li>\r\n            <li><strong>활동</strong>: 만주에서 무장독립투쟁</li>\r\n            <li><strong>조직</strong>: 중광단 (서일) → 북로군정서</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </details>\r\n\r\n      <details open>\r\n        <summary>🏯 불교</summary>\r\n        <div class=\"content\">\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><strong>조직</strong>: 조선불교유신회 (1921)</li>\r\n            <li><strong>지도자</strong>: 한용운</li>\r\n            <li><strong>저작</strong>: '님의 침묵'</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </details>\r\n\r\n      <details open>\r\n        <summary>☯️ 천도교 (동학)</summary>\r\n        <div class=\"content\">\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><strong>활동</strong>: 제2의 3·1운동 (6·10만세운동)</li>\r\n            <li><strong>출판물</strong>: 만세보 창간</li>\r\n            <li><strong>잡지</strong>: 『개벽』, 『신여성』, 『어린이』 간행</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </details>\r\n\r\n      <details open>\r\n        <summary>✝️ 천주교</summary>\r\n        <div class=\"content\">\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><strong>조직</strong>: 의민단 (만주)</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </details>\r\n\r\n      <details open>\r\n        <summary>🕉️ 원불교</summary>\r\n        <div class=\"content\">\r\n          <ul>\r\n            <li><strong>지도자</strong>: 박중빈</li>\r\n            <li><strong>운동</strong>: 새생활 운동 추진</li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </details>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </details>\r",
